{"tid":805220,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"[airsoft]Kwc用Co2罐邊度有得買?","createTime":"2018-09-03T15:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T00:49:13.000Z","uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"63fe556eea70384e1f1aa7cdb09c0f342f655bb9","tid":805220,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:06:53.000Z","msg":"小弟之前玩開Marui green gas槍，想買把KWC P-08玩下，不過未用過Co2 12g罐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網揾香港唔多有得買，會唔會好難保養或者好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以我所知唔可以好似green gas咁由彈匣入氣，每次用完個罐就要即棄，成本會唔會好高？<br />\n<br />\n睇過WE P-08 評價好差( 不過可以green gas彈匣入氣)，通常打幾十槍把槍就報銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇大佬可以指點迷津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3c60c6519b50b576bea5ee78aed9fa69db358d","tid":805220,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:12:32.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ae8827410482ee759221bcf4ee9398f3eff552","tid":805220,"uid":9457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:23:28.000Z","msg":"廣華街通街都係<br />\n平嘅$8一支"},{"pid":"dfeb40d4b70dec41639d6c84ac53259b5b691495","tid":805220,"uid":9457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:24:19.000Z","msg":"題外話 推薦你買Kj 多過 kwc"},{"pid":"333eabb2ad2096475246f263a4c602980025dad0","tid":805220,"uid":9457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:29:20.000Z","msg":"自膠 記錯cz p09<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係落場用 we都還好<br />\n本身平又有個種結構<br />\n同埋呢種槍先天有缺陷<br />\n點樣改都唔係好準<br />\n所以落去睇下睇邊把順眼啲 啱就買啦"},{"pid":"a24f51151bc410b832f60674ce436abb0a60d451","